# Production (committed): values inlined into the GitHub Pages bundle by `vite build`.
# NEVER add API secrets here — Vite inlines every VITE_* variable into the client.
# Provider keys live only in the Cloudflare Worker (wrangler secrets).
#
# Why an absolute URL instead of `/api/ai/chat`?
# GitHub Pages (`manu72.github.io`) cannot route a path to a Cloudflare Worker,
# so production must call the Worker cross-origin. `ALLOWED_ORIGINS` on the
# Worker already includes `https://manu72.github.io`, and the Worker returns
# the correct CORS preflight for that origin.
# If the site ever moves to Cloudflare Pages (or a zone with `/api/*` routed
# to this Worker), revert to the relative path used in `.env`.
VITE_AI_PROXY_URL=https://ayala-ai-proxy.ayalacats.workers.dev/api/ai/chat
VITE_AI_PRIMARY=deepseek
VITE_AI_FALLBACK=openai
